### ============================================================
### ORGANIZER API REQUESTS
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000/v1/organizers
### ============================================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/v1
@authToken = YOUR_ORGANIZER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@organizerId = 1

### ============================================================
### PUBLIC ROUTES (No Authentication Required)
### ============================================================

