### CRUD OPERATIONS
### ============================================================

### Create Organizer Profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/organizers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "business_name": "New Events Company",
    "business_type": "Entertainment",
    "description": "We organize the best entertainment events",
    "website": "https://newevents.com",
    "address": "123 Main Street",
    "city": "Accra",
    "region": "Greater Accra",
    "country": "Ghana",
    "phone": "+233249973054"
}

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Organizer profile created successfully",
#     "data": {
#         "organizer": {...}
#     }
# }

###

### Update Organizer Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/organizers/{{organizerId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "business_name": "Updated Company Name",
    "description": "Updated description"
}

### Expected Response:
